commit message: Replaced the ImageView in the WatorDisplay with a SurfaceView. A bunch of spelling corrections.
Take 'dirty' into account when calculating the versionCode.
Fixed painting the WoldDisplay initially (if there is no painting thread going on that continuously calls WatorDisplay.worldUpdated(...)); removed superfluous semicolon from the gradle build file.

Changed generating gitVersionName and gitVersionCode so that gitVersionCode is generated from the tag but gitVersionName is completely rebuild from the parsed tag; upgraded IntelliJ related project files for IntelliJ 2016
